Introduction

Woo Jewon is a South Korean singer under FirstOne Entertainment. He made his official debut in 2022 as the leader and vocalist of the boy group NINE.I.

Before debuting, Jewon first appeared and competed in the hit survival program "Produce X 101" as a trainee under Around US Entertainment. He finished 54th place and continued training after the show.
